Avast Cleanup Premium 2018 18.1.5172 !{Latest}

Avast Cleanup&#xA0;- a tool for the safe cleaning and optimization of the Windows system, which allows you to increase the speed of your computer.&#xA0;

Safely remove unnecessary data and get rid of garbage tracks to free up space, and also configure the system registry and optimize the system to increase the speed of your computer.

After the analysis is completed, the cleanup tool will display the total number of detected files, the browser cache, add-ons, and the download history and visits.&#xA0;Cleanup shows obsolete programs and driver packages, shared DLLs, and performs system log analysis to free up as much disk space as possible.&#xA0;

Thanks to the built-in scheduler, Avast Cleanup can monitor the computer in real time and detect the remaining files in the system.&#xA0;Additionally, the user can configure the start of cleaning at a specific time so that the process does not affect daily activities.

Avast Cleanup includes everything you need to configure your PC:
&#x2022;&#xA0;Hibernate.&#xA0;A patented setup method takes all of the demanding applications to sleep, so that your PC can run faster.&#xA0;
&#x2022;&#xA0;Shortcut Cleaner.&#xA0;Removes old shortcuts from the desktop and Windows OS logs and other applications.&#xA0;
One click service.&#xA0;Perform 6 critical cleaning and configuration tasks with a single mouse click.&#xA0;
&#x2022;&#xA0;Disk Cleaner.Safely delete files left after running Windows processes and more than 200 of the most common PC programs.&#xA0;
&#x2022;&#xA0;Registry Cleaner.&#xA0;Remove hidden unnecessary data from the Windows registry and fix problems.&#xA0;
&#x2022;&#xA0;Browser Cleaner.&#xA0;Removing residual unnecessary files and cookies from more than 25 browsers, including Edge, Chrome, Firefox and IE.&#xA0;
&#x2022;&#xA0;Settings panel and support center.&#xA0;Quick overview of the status of your PC.&#xA0;
&#x2022;&#xA0;Removing useless resource-intensive software.&#xA0;Detects and removes third-party trial versions, advertisements and toolbars that you do not need.

OS:&#xA0;Windows 10, Windows 8 / 8.1, Windows 7, Vista, XP

